9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Ne Zha 2 | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"After a catastrophic event leaves their bodies destroyed, Ne Zha and Ao Bing are granted a fragile second chance at life. As tensions rise between the dragon clans and celestial forces, the two must undergo a series of perilous trials that will test their bond, challenge their identities, and decide the fate of both mortals and immortals."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/103322/ne-zha-2"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Ne Zha 2"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"After a catastrophic event leaves their bodies destroyed, Ne Zha and Ao Bing are granted a fragile second chance at life. As tensions rise between the dragon clans and celestial forces, the two must undergo a series of perilous trials that will test their bond, challenge their identities, and decide the fate of both mortals and immortals."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/103322/ne-zha-2"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cb5NyNrqiCNNoDkA8FfxHAtypdG.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Ne Zha 2"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"After a catastrophic event leaves their bodies destroyed, Ne Zha and Ao Bing are granted a fragile second chance at life. As tensions rise between the dragon clans and celestial forces, the two must undergo a series of perilous trials that will test their bond, challenge their identities, and decide the fa